  <!-- EN: firefoam pop pack -->
  <Apparel_FirefoampopPack.label>cinturó d’escuma tallafocs</Apparel_FirefoampopPack.label>
  <!-- EN: A utility pack made for firefighters. When triggered, a burst of fire-retardant foam is released, covering a wide circle around its wearer. -->
  <Apparel_FirefoampopPack.description>Una eina pensada per als bombers. Quan es tira una bomba, allibera una ràfega d’escuma tallafocs que cobreix un cercle al voltant de qui la porta.</Apparel_FirefoampopPack.description>
  <!-- EN: firefoam pop -->
  <Apparel_FirefoampopPack.comps.CompReloadable.chargeNoun>bomba d’escuma tallafocs</Apparel_FirefoampopPack.comps.CompReloadable.chargeNoun>
  <!-- EN: on cooldown -->
  <Apparel_FirefoampopPack.comps.CompReloadable.cooldownGerund>en refredament</Apparel_FirefoampopPack.comps.CompReloadable.cooldownGerund>
  <!-- EN: pop firefoam -->
  <Apparel_FirefoampopPack.verbs.pop_firefoam.label>tira escuma tallafocs</Apparel_FirefoampopPack.verbs.pop_firefoam.label>
  
  <!-- EN: smokepop pack -->
  <Apparel_SmokepopBelt.label>cinturó de bombes de fum</Apparel_SmokepopBelt.label>
  <!-- EN: A defensive smokescreen. When activated, it will release a cloud of smoke, obscuring incoming shots and preventing turrets from locking on. -->
  <Apparel_SmokepopBelt.description>Una pantalla de fum defensiva automàtica. Quan el portador és tocat per un projectil, allibera un núvol de fum espès que proporciona cobertura i evita que les torretes metralladores puguin apuntar-lo. Un sol ús.</Apparel_SmokepopBelt.description>
  <!-- EN: smokepop -->
  <Apparel_SmokepopBelt.comps.CompReloadable.chargeNoun>bomba de fum</Apparel_SmokepopBelt.comps.CompReloadable.chargeNoun>
  <!-- EN: on cooldown -->
  <Apparel_SmokepopBelt.comps.CompReloadable.cooldownGerund>en refredament</Apparel_SmokepopBelt.comps.CompReloadable.cooldownGerund>
  <!-- EN: pop smoke -->
  <Apparel_SmokepopBelt.verbs.pop_smoke.label>tira una bomba fum</Apparel_SmokepopBelt.verbs.pop_smoke.label>
  
